title: Mother gives birth in most Massachusetts place possible
text:
Mother gives birth in most Massachusetts place possible 
Published By: Boston.com - Today 
A Massachusetts mother successfully gave birth to a baby girl while stuck in traffic on the Mass Pike on Friday morning, state police said....
